{"tid":226710,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[求屌][長]東京7日獨遊行程","createTime":"2017-05-02T16:46:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-05T22:30:58.000Z","uid":69266,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d52e6b09fbcc84fad88a1175d251da60ffafcbee","tid":226710,"uid":69266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T16:46:46.000Z","msg":"第一日零晨機4,5點到羽田機場,住新宿,會先到酒店放低d野<br />\nDay 1:下北澤<br />\nDay 2:川越，東京大神宮，東京大學<br />\n4點幾出門口去川越,去下冰川神社,川越城本丸御殿,鐘樓,小江戶橫丁,熊野神社果d,之後1430左右走去東京大神宮,行陣再去埋東京大學,夜晚食成藏<br />\nDay 3:鐮倉 + 江之島 <br />\nDay 4:淺草,淺草貓頭鷹cafe, sky tree, 台場<br />\nDay 5:小田原城(朝早坐2粒半鐘車去睇,下晝未plan)<br />\nDay 6:築地＋谷根千<br />\nDay 7:原宿＋澀谷<br />\n<br />\n食就係tabelog搵左d餐廳,但未firm係咪去<br />\n－風雲兒<br />\n－東池袋大勝軒<br />\n－burn side st caf&eacute; <br />\n－花月堂<br />\n－浅草うな鐵，宇奈とと 浅草店<br />\n－尾張屋 <br />\n－成藏<br />\n－治郎丸<br />\n－焼きあご塩らー麺 たかはし 本店 <br />\n－麺屋 一燈<br />\n－無敵家<br />\n－bills<br />\n－尾花<br />\n－Zakuzaku <br />\n－Sugoiniboshiramennagi (新宿,拉麵)<br />\n－鮨国 海膽飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n－Michi (道) <br />\n<br />\n行程會唔會太密<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 第一次plan行程自己去,各位巴絲比下意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56e5221312cd66fb3a3b747a7444061e0948326c","tid":226710,"uid":3748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T17:08:26.000Z","msg":"點解唔住一晚江之島果邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你反正都去埋小田原 <br />\n兩日連埋一齊之後再返東京仲好"},{"pid":"017fd9765eefa8fc29d4fa2fe0cf5463772f5b68","tid":226710,"uid":33727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T17:19:55.000Z","msg":"點解要4點幾出門口 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 未去過川越"},{"pid":"094a22e5ba7cb6a872bde8a99985c352ea5659ab","tid":226710,"uid":69266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T21:58:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解唔住一晚江之島果邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你反正都去埋小田原 <br />\n兩日連埋一齊之後再返東京仲好</blockquote><br />\n懶得再搵酒店 同唔想搬行埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6af1893c3cebbdac693a697254221f533614759","tid":226710,"uid":69266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T22:00:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解要4點幾出門口 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 未去過川越</blockquote><br />\n想去冰川神社拎粒石 所以要勁早起身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"504621ebf6390680d6d32000597ad9f29adfb577","tid":226710,"uid":69266,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T10:31:19.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"453e679855cad702847458222632532c2ea01690","tid":226710,"uid":89411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T11:21:30.000Z","msg":"day4 好chur wo青"},{"pid":"915d590c2eb0b323778f0261fa55a75f67e2c60c","tid":226710,"uid":89411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T11:22:31.000Z","msg":"仲有day7幾點到機場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不如二簡一算"},{"pid":"15648e7f72aec361c7a6e24df77c9af704f89fe7","tid":226710,"uid":34692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T11:25:54.000Z","msg":"day 5 下晝至傍晚可以去橫濱海邊行下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nday6 行程好似相對上比較鬆動"},{"pid":"2e7c7d68f65bd768ce31022f8417e89d87393e1a","tid":226710,"uid":30924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T11:29:10.000Z","msg":"Day 7:原宿＋澀谷  <br />\n<br />\n一日一定唔夠你買..."},{"pid":"24306d9e7a3b2bd2c0f07688e378879141820dbb","tid":226710,"uid":30924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T11:31:01.000Z","msg":"Day 4:淺草,淺草貓頭鷹cafe, sky tree, 台場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSKY TREE 之後再去台埸怕唔怕夜?<br />\nBTW台埸無高達我唔想去"},{"pid":"64922717ea37d139466bb1fa6ea7c4b494711c5b","tid":226710,"uid":54431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T11:38:23.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"386065979edddb0a70aa2c7f0de30514df3fed5e","tid":226710,"uid":30924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T11:46:40.000Z","msg":"我自己<br />\n<br />\nD1 : 又係超早機 , 落機岩岩天光 , 住歌舞APA , 放行季 -&gt;築地埸外-&gt; 行去銀座買少少野-&gt;台埸睇高達 (諗住行outlet , 點知無乜野好買) 直到天黑回酒店<br />\n<br />\nD2: 新宿早餐  -&gt; 迪迪尼海洋 全日<br />\n<br />\nD3: 原宿 全日<br />\n<br />\nD4: 淺草 -&gt; 秋葉原 (太早又無地方去 , 亦唔會再去...)   -&gt; SKY TREE<br />\n<br />\nD5: 吉祥寺-&gt;行去井之頭公園扮英吉 -&gt; 涉谷<br />\n<br />\nD6: 涉谷 , 早一日買唔夠野去補飛 , 之後天黑返機埸走人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n行得極度HEA<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e12b2f995087a47e848418aa23af36519662056","tid":226710,"uid":69266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T15:23:31.000Z","msg":"Day 4 搭零晨機返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實skytree同台場我都唔係太大興趣,都係諗唔到去邊同埋朋友推介先去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該轉做咁<br />\nDay 1:下北澤<br />\nDay 2:川越，東京大神宮，東京大學<br />\nDay 3:鐮倉 + 江之島 <br />\nDay 4:原宿＋澀谷<br />\nDay 5:小田原城+原宿/澀谷<br />\nDay 6:淺草,淺草貓頭鷹cafe, 台場<br />\nDay 7:築地＋谷根千<br />\n同埋青有無d冷門/少人d睇下風景咁地方推介"},{"pid":"5b74eed7775cc0fdcb2a7aeb7e92f0415878a4d6","tid":226710,"uid":69266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T15:50:51.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"8278e608454f8823f6e3e446bbe0328ea7126a61","tid":226710,"uid":89146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T16:32:24.000Z","msg":"留名 打算跟你咁去 懶得編行程<br />\n六月頭去八日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeb69003651047d364ab8b1b4e200acb330e1b20","tid":226710,"uid":20658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T16:44:43.000Z","msg":"下個月我都去東京，住池袋，走果日朝早十點機，即係八點要到機場，想問下各位有咩車咁早返到機場？"},{"pid":"5543cc530000e9aba4b183b3f2edb849a782e227","tid":226710,"uid":21624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T17:23:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下個月我都去東京，住池袋，走果日朝早十點機，即係八點要到機場，想問下各位有咩車咁早返到機場？</blockquote><br />\n你點出機場，就點入返機場<br />\n六點幾咩車都run緊架啦"},{"pid":"5177d91fe627029f5ebf2cdc3b2c660b68e9b7bf","tid":226710,"uid":2997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T22:30:58.000Z","msg":"我會入河口湖一晚"}]}